title: Coleman Hawkins Encounters Ben Webster (Verve1957)
description:
Two giants of jazz saxophone - together.

I once owned this record and loved it. Made me happy when I found it through a torrent SE. Thanks to the anonymous uploader of the single wav these mp3 files are made from. I think the two last tracks may be bonus material for the new edition, not sure.
